{"tid":1866191,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！內媒報道：造謠8君子李文亮病逝","createTime":"2020-02-06T15:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T15:54:35.000Z","uid":249945,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"019406cfdcf8a7523c53bfb5179669904c1e7b40","tid":1866191,"uid":249945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"【突發！內媒報道：造謠8君子李文亮病逝】<br />\n【率先揭發疫情  被公安指造謠訓誡】<br />\n<br />\n多間內地媒體引述消息指，造謠8君子之一的李文亮醫生，周四晚上9時半於重症監護室病逝。<br />\n<br />\n消息指他病情曾一度好轉，但近日突然加重。<br />\n<br />\n李文亮是武漢市中心醫院一名眼科醫生，因最早於12月30日警告外界要注意疫情，而被公安指造謠訓誡。他與另外七名被官方警告的人，一起被外界稱為「造謠8君子」，後來最高法亦為其平反。<br />\n<br />\n他上周接受內地媒體訪問時稱，真相比平反更重要。他亦證實自己在接診時受感染，2月1日確診新型武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n#李文亮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2432295990248206&amp;id=265944843550009&amp;sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2432295990248206%26id%3D265944843550009%26sfnsn%3Dmo&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWfilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=1f6c9752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2432295990248206&amp;id=265944843550009&amp;sfnsn=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e089a8c981f073532098b68cfc78e37542d752ac","tid":1866191,"uid":274149,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:22:09.000Z","msg":"R.I.P<br />\n來生不做中國人"},{"pid":"be0363337254270b498a34edb967e64b5c38b599","tid":1866191,"uid":276989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:22:12.000Z","msg":"喜獲毛主席接見"},{"pid":"1a2e0299a0eab99eb696ac481ba9715daa918f3e","tid":1866191,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:34:39.000Z","msg":"R.A.P.🙏🏻"},{"pid":"80948764ed9b168d43a8525050f586828c851b73","tid":1866191,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T15:39:39.000Z","msg":"R.A.P.🙏🏻"},{"pid":"770096826d399fca200d80d590bae9b77fd51f32","tid":1866191,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":